    "summary": "Fellow exposes a REST Developer API and a remote MCP server; both require workspace-enabled credentials/auth, and no public GraphQL API or CLI was found.",
    "description": "Fellow is an AI meeting assistant that records, transcribes, summarizes, and organizes meeting notes, action items, and related data. It is built for teams and enterprises with governance, privacy, and compliance controls around meeting records.",
